Published Friday, March 7th, 2025
íŸ@eaa37c03360f866e42865e19e351fa556797ef1d833ccfadf13a8b00c501df33⁄âTitle: title: 'This week in Nushell #289'
Path: Highlights
Content:
The Nushell repo reached 10,000 commits this week with the addition of an LSP fix by blindFS. Thank you again for the

steady stream of LSP and Treesitter improvements!
Congrats to the YAML family! 
``to yaml``
 welcomes new sibling 
``to yml``
 so that 
``save``
ing files with either extension

works seamlessly. Thanks LoicReigel!
Thanks MMesch for multiple Polars PRs this week!
And 
ayamdobhal
 brings some great improvements to 
``random uuid``
 with the addition of 4 new UUID version implementations.

Thank you!
As always, here's the full list of commits for the week ...
íŸ@9958da1aee66a9991f240ed5a09c1dbce13df2921d4e7c40debe95eccb85fc8c⁄XTitle: title: 'This week in Nushell #289'
Path: Nushell
Content:
blindFS
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15263] Fixed a security audit issue by bumping the 
``ring``
 dependency
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15247] Made LSP completion items respect the 
``append_whitespace``
 flag
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15238] Fixed LSP completion for commands with following text
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15233] Added manually triggered signature help in LSP
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15226] Fixed LSP completion label descriptions for 
``cell_path``
 and external values
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15188] Fixed LSP completion for commands defined after the cursor
LoicRiegel
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15254] Added a 
``to yml``
 command
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15234] Clarified trailing line ending in 
``to json -r``
 documentation
MMesch
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15250] Enhanced polars plugin documentation
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15249] Added 
``Xor``
 to polars plugin nu_expressions
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15248] Added 
``And``
 and 
``Or``
 operators to polars plugin nu_expressions
ysthakur
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15246] Fixed an unterminated loop in 
``parse_record``
ayamdobhal
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15239] Added support for UUID versions other than 4 in 
``random uuid``
sgvictorino
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15230] Prevented panic when parsing incomplete multi-expr 
``|``
 matches
hustcer
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15221] Added ANSI codes for cursor movement
hardfau1t
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15213] Fixed 
``compact``
 for empty lists or records in columns
WindSoilder
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15206] Added a helpful message for frozen jobs
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/15126] Fixed 
``$env.FILE_PWD``
 and 
``$env.CURRENT_FILE``
 inside overlay use
